data.description: Ready to fish and watch the sunset over the river from your own spacious deck? With an attached guest room including full bath and private entrance, you will be able to share the joys of life on the river! Fenced backyard and professional landscaping add to the beautiful finishes inside, all brand new within the last few years! 10 year warranty on hot water heater, 30 year architectural roof new in 2020. BRAND NEW HVAC 2022 Dehumidifier, sump pump, crawl encapsulation and siding in 2020. Updated kitchen with 2023 Gas stove and cabinet pull-outs as well as baths stylishly updated. DR and LR new dry wall and fresh paint 2021. Schedule your tour of this waterfront beauty today! *** On top or all that, sellers have a 2.75 ASSUMABLE loan!!!
